<subSubSection pageId="169" pageNumber="170" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="169.[151,1437,824,994]" pageId="169" pageNumber="170">
This family of acalyptrate flies contains 72, predominantly Palaearctic, species (
<bibRefCitation author="Marshall, S. A." box="[1059,1228,860,886]" pageId="169" pageNumber="170" refId="ref358584" refString="Marshall, S. A. (2012) Flies. The natural history and diversity of Diptera. Firefly Books, Richmond Hill, 616 pp." type="book" year="2012">Marshall 2012</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Pape, T." pageId="169" pageNumber="170" refId="ref350035" refString="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Pape, T. (2020) Systema Dipterorum. Version 2. 7. Available from: http: // www. diptera. org / (accessed 30 August 2020)" type="url" year="2020">Evenhuis &amp; Pape 2020</bibRefCitation>
). In his “ 
<emphasis box="[321,527,896,922]" italics="true" pageId="169" pageNumber="170">Stirps Loncheinae</emphasis>
”, rather than in the family 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Loew" authorityYear="1862" box="[848,999,896,922]" class="Insecta" family="Pallopteridae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="169" pageNumber="170" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Pallopteridae</taxonomicName>
, proposed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Loew, H." box="[1162,1327,896,923]" pageId="169" pageNumber="170" refId="ref356539" refString="Loew, H. (1862 b) Die europaischen Bohrfliegen (Trypetidae). Kaiserlich-Konigliche Staatsdruckerei, Wien, 128 pp. + 26 pls." type="book" year="1862">Loew (1862b)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." pageId="169" pageNumber="170" pagination="243 - 274" refId="ref370928" refString="Rondani, C. (1875 a) Species italicae ordinis dipterorum (Muscaria Rndn.) collectae et observatae. Stirps XXII Lonchaeinae Rndn. Bullettino della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 6 (4) [1874], 243 - 274." type="journal article" year="1875">Rondani (1875a)</bibRefCitation>
described one Palaearctic species, considered as a junior synonym (
<bibRefCitation author="Morge, G." box="[1024,1169,932,958]" pageId="169" pageNumber="170" refId="ref360435" refString="Morge, G. (1984) Family Pallopteridae. In: Soos, A. &amp; Papp, L. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Diptera. Volume 9. Micropezidae - Agromyzidae. Elsevier Science Publishers, Amsterdam &amp; Akademiai Kiado, Budapest, pp. 242 - 246." type="book" year="1984">Morge 1984</bibRefCitation>
). No 
<typeStatus box="[1234,1282,933,959]" pageId="169" pageNumber="170">type</typeStatus>
material was located in this study and is presumed lost.
</paragraph>
